data.description: This stunning home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2 car garage, and an in-ground pool. The spacious great room includes a fireplace, built-in bookshelves, and a wet bar, perfect for entertaining guests. The kitchen provides ample cabinet and counter space, a breakfast nook, breakfast bar, and French doors leading to the enclosed patio/sunroom. Adjacent to the kitchen is a formal dining room, small office area and laundry room. Large primary bedroom boasts a seating area, makeup table, ensuite bath, and walk-in closet. The guest rooms are spacious with large closets. Outside, the enclosed patio leads to an outdoor living space and an in-ground pool. Additional amenities include wood flooring, sprinkler system, established landscaping, mature trees, and more. Call to schedule your showing today!
